-39f7-dd09-a1bf-3bffa9680001</guid></item><item><title>我在那里。在卡法阿扎。对加沙的狂轰乱炸不是解决办法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/i-was-there-in-kfar-azza-indiscriminate-bombing-of-gaza-is-not-the-solution/0000018b-3990-d0ac-a39f-b9921c5a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 21:13:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/i-was-there-in-kfar-azza-indiscriminate-bombing-of-gaza-is-not-the-solution/0000018b-3990-d0ac-a39f-b9921c5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妄图推翻哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-illusion-of-toppling-hamas/0000018b-39f5-dd09-a1bf-3bfd4ca90000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 21:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-illusion-of-toppling-hamas/0000018b-39f5-dd09-a1bf-3bfd4ca90000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发布了法裔以色列人质的视频，这是加沙的第一个生命迹象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/hamas-releases-first-video-of-israeli-hostage-in-gaza/0000018b-39ff-d450-a3af-79ffc8a50000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，“哈马斯试图将自己描绘成一个人道组织，但它却对谋杀和绑架婴儿、妇女、儿童和老人负有责任”</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 20:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/hamas-releases-first-video-of-israeli-hostage-in-gaza/0000018b-39ff-d450-a3af-79ffc8a50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列哈马斯战争表明拜登：你无法逃离中东</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-16/ty-article/.highlight/israel-hamas-war-shows-biden-you-cant-escape-the-middle-east/0000018b-39c5-d5b8-a78b-f9d57f470000</link><description>拜登现在正在吸取自 1948 年以来每一位美国总统都学到的教训：无论你喜欢与否，以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突最终都会找到你的家门口</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 19:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-16/ty-article/.highlight/israel-hamas-war-shows-biden-you-cant-escape-the-middle-east/0000018b-39c5-d5b8-a78b-f9d57f470000</guid></item><item><title>英国首相确认六名英国国民在以色列哈马斯“大屠杀”中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/british-pm-confirms-six-u-k-nationals-among-dead-from-hamas-pogrom-in-israel/0000018b-393d-d450-a3af-793d4fb60000</link><description>周一，英国首相苏纳克在伦敦下议院发表讲话，称一周前周六对一系列以色列边境社区的袭击是一场“大屠杀”，并补充说，在军事回应中，“以色列必须在符合国际人道主义法”</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 16:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/british-pm-confirms-six-u-k-nationals-among-dead-from-hamas-pogrom-in-israel/0000018b-393d-d450-a3af-793d4fb60000</guid></item><item><title>“非常非常复杂的心情”：美国国民乘坐紧急巡航逃离以色列-哈马斯战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-weird-way-to-travel-mixed-emotions-among-americans-as-emergency-boat-leaves-israel/0000018b-38d9-d450-a3af-79ddfb1e0000</link><description>周一从海法前往塞浦路斯进行五星级度假的美国公民的气氛令人疲惫。有些人不想离开，另一些人则迫不及待地想离开——所有人都想知道他们是否要为此付出代价</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 16:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-weird-way-to-travel-mixed-emotions-among-americans-as-emergency-boat-leaves-israel/0000018b-38d9-d450-a3af-79ddfb1e0000</guid></item><item><title>对袭击的震惊，对失败的愤怒：内塔尼亚胡的支持率如何在以色列跌至谷底</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/how-netanyahus-approval-ratings-have-hit-rock-bottom-in-israel/0000018b-38b3-dd09-a1bf-3abb69c70000</link><description>新的民意调查显示，以色列人认为哈马斯的袭击暴露了国内“领导层崩溃”；三分之二的人实际上更喜欢除内塔尼亚胡之外的任何人担任以色列下一任总理。但是，就像他们的政府一样，以色列人对战后加沙的愿景是模糊的</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 16:33:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/how-netanyahus-approval-ratings-have-hit-rock-bottom-in-israel/0000018b-38b3-dd09-a1bf-3abb69c70000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处收回指控哈马斯从加沙大院窃取人道主义援助的声明</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-16/ty-article/unrwa-nixes-statement-accusing-hamas-of-stealing-humanitarian-fuel-from-gaza-compound/0000018b-38fa-d0ac-a39f-b9fa2f1c0000</link><description>联合国致力于巴勒斯坦难民的机构周日表示，它无法再提供人道主义援助，并警告加沙正在耗尽食物、水和药品</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 15:37:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-16/ty-article/unrwa-nixes-statement-accusing-hamas-of-stealing-humanitarian-fuel-from-gaza-compound/0000018b-38fa-d0ac-a39f-b9fa2f1c0000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属向红十字会求助：被关押在加沙的近200名以色列人中有许多人急需医疗救治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/many-of-almost-200-israelis-held-in-gaza-in-severe-need-of-medical-treatment/0000018b-38b8-d0ac-a39f-b9bad3600000</link><description>人质和失踪家庭论坛在给红十字国际委员会的一封信中表示，被哈马斯关押的人仍然“面临严重并发症的风险，他们承受着难以想象的痛苦”</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 14:47:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/many-of-almost-200-israelis-held-in-gaza-in-severe-need-of-medical-treatment/0000018b-38b8-d0ac-a39f-b9bad3600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列允许水通过拉法过境点进入加沙地带，但不允许燃料和食物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-allows-water-into-gaza-strip-via-the-rafah-crossing-but-no-fuel-nor-food/0000018b-3809-dd09-a1bf-3aa96cd70000</link><description>在埃及监管下通过卡车运送的人道主义援助物资不包括燃料和食品。以色列国防官员表示，“只允许向加沙地带南部地区输送水，该地区已被指定为人道主义疏散区”</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 14:26:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-allows-water-into-gaza-strip-via-the-rafah-crossing-but-no-fuel-nor-food/0000018b-3809-dd09-a1bf-3aa96cd70000</guid></item><item><title>要么打击哈马斯，要么逃跑：以色列人在战争期间逃离该国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fight-or-flight-after-hamas-attacked-these-israelis-fled-the-country/0000018b-3876-d450-a3af-797e47690000</link><description>从罗马到塞浦路斯和希腊：除了成千上万在战争爆发时回国的以色列人之外，还有许多人在该国正面临最困难的时期之一时前往国外。价格</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 13:59:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fight-or-flight-after-hamas-attacked-these-israelis-fled-the-country/0000018b-3876-d450-a3af-797e47690000</guid></item><item><title>向以色列空运武器、轰炸机飞往约旦、两艘航母：美国向中东部署更多部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-16/ty-article/airlift-to-israel-bombers-in-jordan-two-carriers-u-s-deploying-more-forces-to-mideast/0000018b-385d-d450-a3af-795de1010000</link><description>开源飞行跟踪和卫星图像显示，该地区部署了先进的武器、防空系统以及数十架战斗轰炸机、情报收集平台和重型货运飞机，试图阻止伊朗和真主党在以色列北部开辟第二条战线</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 13:32:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-16/ty-article/airlift-to-israel-bombers-in-jordan-two-carriers-u-s-deploying-more-forces-to-mideast/0000018b-385d-d450-a3af-795de1010000</guid></item><item><title>我们犹太人需要听到穆斯林领导人谴责哈马斯的暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-jews-need-to-hear-muslim-leaders-denounce-hamas-atrocities/0000018b-3777-d450-a3af-7f7fc0660000</link><description>当务之急是与巴勒斯坦人和那些与我们有着同样恐惧的阿拉伯和穆斯林世界的人们找到共同的事业。我们需要从阿拉伯领导人、伊玛目和穆斯林学者那里听到，这是对真正伊斯兰教的耻辱</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 13:30:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-jews-need-to-hear-muslim-leaders-denounce-hamas-atrocities/0000018b-3777-d450-a3af-7f7fc0660000</guid></item></channel></rss>